<h1>Parameters of Night Time Video Profile</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Description</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>As we know the lighting condition affects the video quality strongly in camera. To have better presentation of the video in the camera, many algorithms of image processing are proposed. In PlatformT camera, except utilizing the sensor/DSP capabilities of the day/night handler function, the camera provides the change of video parameters according to its day/night state. This helps the camera to adapt itself widely in the applications.</p>
  <p>The parameters of the video profile for night time state are defined here. Every parameter has the corresponding URL to access. These URLs are located in the ENCODER CGI.</p>
</blockquote>
